{"tid":2097017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《港區國安法第43條實施細則》：2. 限制受調查的人離開香港","createTime":"2020-07-06T13:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T13:58:28.000Z","uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6641e32b9b0c90a4b572f352c5a961a33ab6be0f","tid":2097017,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"參照現行《防止賄賂條例》（第201章）限制受調查人離境的條文，細則授權警務人員可向裁判官申請手令，要求懷疑犯了該等危害國家安全罪行而受調查的人交出旅行證件，並限制其離開香港，以免部分涉案人士潛逃海外。交出旅行證件的人，可以書面向警務處處長或裁判官申請發還該旅行證件及批准離開香港。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n依家調查下就可以叫你交passport，唔使落案拉上法庭鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"117fb416503f92206da63ba09ea5d39adbad0683","tid":2097017,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"即係軟禁"},{"pid":"442fac9dec56c5e4445cadf16757ceb1452d311c","tid":2097017,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}